ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectLa Chambre de Commerce de Montmagny (Quebec) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by LA CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE MONTMAGNY, in Quebec, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES of its district from the town and county of Montmagny, excluding the municipality of St-Paul and the municipality of Cap St-Ignace, to all the municipalities of the MRC of Montmagny (Montmagny, Saint-Antoine-de-l'Isle-aux-Grues, Cap-Saint-Ignace, Berthier-sur-Mer, Saint-Pierre-de-la-Rivière-du-Sud, Saint-François-de-la-Rivière-du-Sud, Sainte-Euphémie-de-la-Rivière-du-Sud, Notre-Dame-du-Rosaire, Sainte-Apolline-de-Patton, Saint-Fabien-de-Panet, Sainte-Lucie-de-Beauregard, Lac-Frontière, Saint-Just-de-Bretenières, Saint-Paul-de-Montminy).
